/Users/zhanglongqin/AuditHoundV2/output/88mph_dualmodel_1round_p4/rounds/round_1/merge_stderr.log:551:{"findings":[{"id":"F-001","severity":"Critical","confidence":"high","title":"Anyone can reinitialize the NFT contracts and seize deposit/funding token ownership","locations":["onchain_auto/0xf0b7de03134857391d8d43ed48e20edf21461097/contracts/NFT.sol:39","onchain_auto/0xf0b7de03134857391d8d43ed48e20edf21461097/contracts/NFT.sol:44","onchain_auto/0xf0b7de03134857391d8d43ed48e20edf21461097/contracts/NFT.sol:79","onchain_auto/0xf0b7de03134857391d8d43ed48e20edf21461097/contracts/NFT.sol:83","onchain_auto/0xf0b7de03134857391d8d43ed48e20edf21461097/contracts/DInterest.sol:770","onchain_auto/0xf0b7de03134857391d8d43ed48e20edf21461097/contracts/DInterest.sol:903","onchain_auto/0xf0b7de03134857391d8d43ed48e20edf21461097/contracts/DInterestWithDepositFee.sol:801","onchain_auto/0xf0b7de03134857391d8d43ed48e20edf21461097/contracts/DInterestWithDepositFee.sol:934"],"claim":"`NFT.init()` is external and has neither a one-time initialization guard nor access control, so any account can call it on an already-deployed deposit or funding NFT clone and transfer contract ownership to itself. The new owner then gains the owner-only `mint`/`burn` powers over the live position NFTs relied on by the pools.","impact":"An attacker can take over a pool's `depositNFT` or `fundingNFT`, burn users' position tokens, block future minting, and break the ownership checks used during withdrawals and funder payouts. This can permanently lock depositor and funder claims and DoS the pool.","paths":["Call `NFT.init(attacker, ...)` on the deployed deposit NFT or funding NFT contract.","As the new owner, call `burn(tokenId)` on victim deposit/funding NFTs or interfere with future minting.","Victim `withdraw()` / funder payout paths revert when `ownerOf()` no longer returns a valid holder for the expected NFT."],"round":1,"source_agents":["codex_1"]},{"id":"F-002","severity":"High","confidence":"high","titl