I’ve narrowed this to two realistic public routes: a zero-fee Balancer-funded `vault.earn()` deposit sandwich for the idle 32.6k DAI already in the vault, and a dual-token Balancer route that uses public `vault.withdraw(shares)` to reach the strategy’s zero-min exit path after `earn()` drains idle cash. I’m editing the verifier now around those atomic attempts so failed sizes revert cleanly and don’t poison later tries.
